807
00:47:24,367 --> 00:47:26,932
Ce-Ce hasn't come back yet,
now I'm worried about Eddie.

808
00:47:26,932 --> 00:47:28,002
He left the house?

809
00:47:28,002 --> 00:47:30,006
Yeah. He went to go get some water,

810
00:47:30,006 --> 00:47:32,402
but, he still hasn't come back yet.

811
00:47:32,402 --> 00:47:33,735
I was about to go look for him.

812
00:47:33,735 --> 00:47:35,476
No, you mustn't.

813
00:47:35,476 --> 00:47:38,126
Why not? I mean I just
can't leave them out there.

814
00:47:38,126 --> 00:47:39,598
[Kadja] You won't be safe.

815
00:47:39,598 --> 00:47:41,621
But, what about the others?

816
00:47:41,621 --> 00:47:43,555
It's too late.

817
00:47:43,555 --> 00:47:44,791
Now what are you sayin'?

818
00:47:44,791 --> 00:47:48,008
I tried to warn you,
but you wouldn't listen.

819
00:47:48,008 --> 00:47:49,778
Your friends are gone and you will be too

820
00:47:49,778 --> 00:47:52,221
