821
00:47:52,221 --> 00:47:53,554
- Who?
- Killjoy!

822
00:47:55,135 --> 00:47:55,968
Killjoy?

823
00:47:57,175 --> 00:48:01,789
(scoffs) I mean even if I
believed in this shit, why?

824
00:48:01,789 --> 00:48:03,828
Why is he coming?

825
00:48:03,828 --> 00:48:05,797
Tell them about it, Nick.

826
00:48:05,797 --> 00:48:09,797
They need to know.
(clock ticks)

827
00:48:11,513 --> 00:48:14,346
What is she talking about, Nick?

828
00:48:15,273 --> 00:48:16,106
Nick?

829
