What?

830
00:48:18,866 --> 00:48:20,845
I was just trying to help Ray-Ray out.

831
00:48:20,845 --> 00:48:22,616
Damn you, Nick!

832
00:48:22,616 --> 00:48:25,453
Look, Ce-Ce and I
went out into the woods,

833
00:48:25,453 --> 00:48:28,484
she did some kind of
ceremony thing, I don't know.

834
00:48:28,484 --> 00:48:29,858
Is that true?

835
00:48:29,858 --> 00:48:32,759
Yeah, but it didn't
work, it was all bullshit.

836
00:48:32,759 --> 00:48:34,410
Yeah, well where is Ce-Ce?

837
00:48:34,410 --> 00:48:36,546
Look, I told you I don't know!

838
00:48:36,546 --> 00:48:37,461
All right, we got into an argument

839
00:48:37,461 --> 00:48:39,578
