840
00:48:39,578 --> 00:48:40,906
It's the last I saw of her.

841
00:48:40,906 --> 00:48:42,562
Why didn't you say something?

842
00:48:42,562 --> 00:48:43,479
Say what?

843
00:48:45,224 --> 00:48:49,126
You don't actually believe
Killjoy exists, much do you?

844
00:48:49,126 --> 00:48:51,062
I don't know, okay?

845
00:48:51,062 --> 00:48:53,067
All I know is that I
don't know where Ce-Ce is,

846
00:48:53,067 --> 00:48:54,967
and I don't know where Eddie is.

847
00:48:54,967 --> 00:48:57,300
I don't know where they are.

848
00:48:58,459 --> 00:49:00,042
Jesus Christ, Nick.

849
00:49:01,337 --> 00:49:03,823
