850
00:49:03,823 --> 00:49:06,624
I don't believe in this
Voodoo bullshit anyway.

851
00:49:06,624 --> 00:49:09,207
You know what, man? Fuck y'all.

852
00:49:10,539 --> 00:49:13,289
Wait! We're not gonna split up.

853
00:49:15,044 --> 00:49:18,472
