857
00:49:30,864 --> 00:49:33,235
That sure sounds like a good idea to me.

858
00:49:33,235 --> 00:49:37,402
(chuckles) Somethin' like that.

859
00:49:42,893 --> 00:49:47,060
(insects chirping)
(suspenseful music)

860
00:49:50,989 --> 00:49:54,100
(Killjoy laughs)

861
00:49:54,100 --> 00:49:55,850
Ce-Ce, is that you?

862
00:49:57,364 --> 00:50:02,255
Look, I'm sorry about what
happened earlier, all right?

863
00:50:02,255 --> 00:50:04,754
(Killjoy laughs)

864
00:50:04,754 --> 00:50:06,973
Is that you, Eddie?

865
00:50:06,973 --> 00:50:09,102
Man, ain't no time for your bullshit.

866
00:50:09,102 --> 00:50:12,021
Shit ain't funny, man,
quit clownin' around.

867
00:50:12,021 --> 00:50:16,188
(laughs) I think it's
real funny, brother.

868
00:50:18,135 --> 00:50:20,218
(laughs)

869
00:50:25,862 --> 00:50:27,878
What the fuck are you supposed to be?

870
00:50:27,878 --> 00:50:32,045
Me? I'm the one you and
your girlfriend asked for.

871
00:50:32,995 --> 00:50:36,215
She was sweet, by the way. (Laughs)

872
00:50:36,215 --> 00:50:37,408
Man, where is she?

873
00:50:37,408 --> 00:50:41,241
Who, her? I tore off
a piece of that myself.

874
00:50:42,280 --> 00:50:47,061
