875
00:50:47,061 --> 00:50:49,061
And now, it's your turn.

876
00:50:51,412 --> 00:50:53,357
Turn for what, man?

877
00:50:53,357 --> 00:50:56,274
(laughs) To die.

878
00:50:58,201 --> 00:51:02,368
Shit, I don't think so,
my circus freak brother.

879
00:51:03,296 --> 00:51:06,647
Oh, don't shoot. No, no, no, no, no, no.

880
00:51:06,647 --> 00:51:10,814
(gunfire)
(Killjoy groans)

881
00:51:12,681 --> 00:51:15,264
(laughs, tsks)

882
00:51:16,526 --> 00:51:18,236
What the fuck?

883
00:51:18,236 --> 00:51:20,319
(laughs)

884
00:51:24,873 --> 00:51:29,745
Missed me, missed me, now
you've gotta kiss me. (Kiss)

885
00:51:29,745 --> 00:51:32,132
Fuck it. Guns are for
pussies anyway, man.

886
00:51:32,132 --> 00:51:34,303
I'm gonna cut that fuckin'
smile off your face.

887
00:51:34,303 --> 00:51:36,036
Aw, don't you know a smile is just

888
00:51:36,036 --> 00:51:38,703
