889
00:51:40,041 --> 00:51:42,374
I told you it's time to die.

890
00:51:46,780 --> 00:51:47,613
Here.

891
00:51:49,065 --> 00:51:49,898
Oh?

892
00:51:54,261 --> 00:51:56,344
(laughs)

893
00:51:58,317 --> 00:51:59,150
[Nick] What the hell are you doin',

894
00:51:59,150 --> 00:52:01,233
you fuckin' Bozo wannabe?

895
00:52:06,462 --> 00:52:07,295
(grunts)

896
00:52:07,295 --> 00:52:09,378
I'm not doing anything.

897
00:52:10,440 --> 00:52:14,607
Your life appears to be
in your hands. (Laughs)

898
00:52:16,046 --> 00:52:18,434
Ah!
(Nick grunts)

899
00:52:18,434 --> 00:52:20,846
Oh, that's gotta hurt.

900
00:52:20,846 --> 00:52:25,317
Ooh, ooh, let's give you a
smiley face, come on, come on!

901
00:52:25,317 --> 00:52:27,300
(both shouting)

902
00:52:27,300 --> 00:52:29,686
Ooh, does that hurt? Does it, does it?

903
00:52:29,686 --> 00:52:30,853
Perhaps again.

904
00:52:32,669 --> 00:52:34,738
Ah!
(Nick grunts)

905
00:52:34,738 --> 00:52:37,215
Ooh, are you bleeding, are you bleeding?

906
00:52:37,215 --> 00:52:39,895
Yes you are, good. (Laughs)

907
00:52:39,895 --> 00:52:42,069
How 'bout one more?

908
00:52:42,069 --> 00:52:44,362
Oh, you still have an eye left.

909
00:52:44,362 --> 00:52:48,056
Let me see what I can
do about that. (Grunts)

910
00:52:48,056 --> 00:52:50,556
(Nick grunts)

911
00:52:51,463 --> 00:52:53,546
(laughs)

912
00:52:54,706 --> 00:52:57,039
Oh, come on now baby, smile.

913
00:53:00,039 --> 00:53:04,206
People need to get more
fun out of death. (Laughs)

914
00:53:20,447 --> 00:53:23,499
Lost in darkness, in secrets concealed,

915
00:53:23,499 --> 00:53:26,999
we plead with thee, let truth be revealed.

916
00:53:29,687 --> 00:53:32,937
Lost in darkness, in secrets concealed,

917
00:53:34,054 --> 00:53:37,554
we plead with thee, let truth be revealed.

918
00:53:38,806 --> 00:53:42,056
Lost in darkness, in secrets concealed,

919
00:53:44,184 --> 00:53:47,693
we plead with thee, let truth be revealed.

920
00:53:47,693 --> 00:53:48,881
(suspenseful music)

921
00:53:48,881 --> 00:53:50,367
Lost in darkness...

922
00:53:50,367 --> 00:53:52,521
Are you sure this thing is working?

923
00:53:52,521 --> 00:53:55,738
(chuckles) Oh, it's working all right.

924
00:53:55,738 --> 00:53:57,988
I can feel him, he is near.

925
00:54:02,305 --> 00:54:03,472
Are you ready>

926
00:54:06,822 --> 00:54:08,489
Yeah, we're ready.

927
00:54:20,357 --> 00:54:21,607
Now you come.

928
00:54:34,969 --> 00:54:38,856
Charlotte, come on,
we have to trust Kadja,

929
00:54:38,856 --> 00:54:42,023
she knows what she's doing. It's okay.

930
00:54:50,837 --> 00:54:52,837
(gasps)

931
00:55:11,446 --> 00:55:14,196
(Killjoy laughs)

932
00:55:17,635 --> 00:55:18,555
What was that?

933
00:55:18,555 --> 00:55:22,508
(chuckles) it's him, it's Killjoy.

934
00:55:22,508 --> 00:55:24,456
What does he want from us?

935
00:55:24,456 --> 00:55:28,383
He wants all of us, and
his power is very strong.

936
00:55:28,383 --> 00:55:32,338
(Killjoy laughs)
(skull buzzes)

937
00:55:32,338 --> 00:55:36,505
[Killjoy] Come out, come
out, wherever you are. (Laughs)

938
00:55:38,860 --> 00:55:41,527
Shut up, shut up, you shut up!

939
00:55:43,206 --> 00:55:46,850
(chuckles) That's nothing.

940
00:55:46,850 --> 00:55:48,237
Mere tricks.

941
00:55:48,237 --> 00:55:50,289
Oh, Killjoy's quite a prankster.

942
00:55:50,289 --> 00:55:54,078
