before moving in for the kill.

943
00:55:54,078 --> 00:55:57,610
(chuckles) But, we'll see
who'll have the last laugh.

944
00:55:57,610 --> 00:55:59,606
[Denise] What do we do?

945
00:55:59,606 --> 00:56:01,106
I must face him.

946
00:56:02,232 --> 00:56:05,815
You stay here in the
house, you'll be safe.

947
00:56:08,078 --> 00:56:11,218
Listen, I can't let you
go out there all alone.

948
00:56:11,218 --> 00:56:12,885
[Kadja] Very well.

949
00:56:15,308 --> 00:56:19,124
Listen, Charlotte, you
just stay in the house, okay?

950
00:56:19,124 --> 00:56:21,123
Kadja said it's safe here.

951
00:56:21,123 --> 00:56:23,809
You just find yourself a place to hide.

952
00:56:23,809 --> 00:56:26,809
