955
00:56:32,647 --> 00:56:35,407
But, you just stay here, you'll be safe.

956
00:56:35,407 --> 00:56:36,574
We'll be back.

957
00:56:37,870 --> 00:56:40,203
Here, for your protection.

958
00:56:44,774 --> 00:56:47,774
