963
00:57:29,033 --> 00:57:30,756
You better find a place to hide yourself,

964
00:57:30,756 --> 00:57:32,989
you shouldn't let him see you!

965
00:57:32,989 --> 00:57:35,717
I'll deal with this thing from here.

966
00:57:35,717 --> 00:57:37,717
- But...
- Go, hide now!

967
00:57:41,448 --> 00:57:43,531
(sniffs)

968
00:57:45,326 --> 00:57:47,997
[Killjoy] Here, piggy,
piggy, piggy, piggy, piggy.

969
00:57:47,997 --> 00:57:51,691
Here, piggy. I know
you're out here somewhere.

970
00:57:51,691 --> 00:57:54,608
Hello? Where are you, little piggy?

971
00:57:57,270 --> 00:58:01,437
Come out, come out,
wherever you are. (Laughs)

972
00:58:02,573 --> 00:58:04,671
Come out!
(Denise gasps)

973
00:58:04,671 --> 00:58:07,588
Come on, piggy, don't be a chicken.

974
00:58:08,675 --> 00:58:12,842
(clucks) Come out. (Clucks)

975
00:58:14,148 --> 00:58:18,315
