977
00:58:34,732 --> 00:58:35,899
Where are you?

978
00:58:38,197 --> 00:58:41,030
(breathes deeply)

979
00:58:43,170 --> 00:58:46,503
Lord of the spirits, to you I do call.

980
00:58:49,361 --> 00:58:53,901
Lord of the night, of the
moon, of the stars, hear me!

981
00:58:53,901 --> 00:58:56,754
I was going to save
you for last. (Laughs)

982
00:58:56,754 --> 00:59:01,109
This is going far enough,
I won't let you hurt them!

983
00:59:01,109 --> 00:59:04,742
Well, you know, I've got things to do,

984
00:59:04,742 --> 00:59:08,159
people to kill. (Laughs)

985
00:59:13,885 --> 00:59:16,512
(suspenseful music)

986
00:59:16,512 --> 00:59:18,512
(gasps)

987
00:59:20,067 --> 00:59:22,418
[Charlotte] It's me! Miss
Martinez, it's me, it's me.

988
00:59:22,418 --> 00:59:26,585
Calma, we gotta get out of
here before he comes back.

989
00:59:28,377 --> 00:59:29,210
Where did you go?

990
00:59:29,210 --> 00:59:30,270
Is not important.

991
00:59:30,270 --> 00:59:32,136
Come on, you've gotta
get back in the house.

992
00:59:32,136 --> 00:59:34,835
I know. We gotta get outta
here, come on, let's go.

993
00:59:34,835 --> 00:59:35,752
Let's go.

994
00:59:40,545 --> 00:59:44,253
Get back, you devil,
I'm not afraid of you.

995
00:59:44,253 --> 00:59:48,420
Come on, baby, is that the
best you've got? (Laughs)

996
00:59:52,197 --> 00:59:54,447
(rumbling)

997
00:59:55,408 --> 00:59:56,991
Ooh, what was that?

998
00:59:59,458 --> 01:00:02,708
You're on your way to
hell where you belong!

999
01:00:02,708 --> 01:00:03,625
Ooh, hmm.

1000
01:00:05,337 --> 01:00:07,087
Well, let's see here.

1001
01:00:08,149 --> 01:00:09,982
What shall I wish for?

1002
01:00:22,045 --> 01:00:25,697
Why don't you quit while you're ahead?

1003
