No! (Screams)
(Killjoy laughs)

1004
01:00:34,388 --> 01:00:37,471
(strangles, shrieks)

1005
01:00:43,828 --> 01:00:44,882
What are we gonna do?

1006
01:00:44,882 --> 01:00:46,215
Lock the door.

1007
01:00:52,632 --> 01:00:57,025
