Come on, you sick fuck!

1016
01:01:26,933 --> 01:01:27,850
Whoo, oh!

1017
01:01:29,133 --> 01:01:31,725
So, you like to play rough, huh?

1018
01:01:31,725 --> 01:01:35,892
Good. I like spunky girls. (Laughs)

1019
01:01:37,531 --> 01:01:39,519
I'm not goin' down that easy.

1020
01:01:39,519 --> 01:01:41,019
Oh, yes you are.

1021
01:01:43,987 --> 01:01:46,070
(laughs)

1022
01:01:47,727 --> 01:01:49,256
What's that you say?

1023
01:01:49,256 --> 01:01:53,423
Can't we all just get along? (Laughs)

1024
01:01:55,604 --> 01:01:57,995
Leave me alone, you psycho circus.

1025
01:01:57,995 --> 01:02:02,162
(laughs) You. You have been
a very, very naughty girl,

1026
01:02:04,949 --> 01:02:06,799
haven't you, Charlotte?

1027
01:02:06,799 --> 01:02:10,966
