to naughty girls, don't we?

1028
01:02:15,004 --> 01:02:19,142
Lord of the black
spirit, to you I do call.

1029
01:02:19,142 --> 01:02:20,642
Lord of the night.

1030
01:02:21,967 --> 01:02:24,588
Yes, smartass, go ahead, go on.

1031
01:02:24,588 --> 01:02:28,783
Lord of the night, of
the moon, of the stars,

1032
01:02:28,783 --> 01:02:29,616
hear me,

1033
01:02:30,691 --> 01:02:31,524
hear me.

1034
01:02:33,650 --> 01:02:34,655
Lord of the night...

1035
